WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.610 --> 00:00:10.320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So. what do you want me to draw and where?</font>

2
00:00:10.320 --> 00:00:11.320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

3
00:00:11.570 --> 00:00:12.700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

4
00:00:12.700 --> 00:00:14.540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with the facepaint?!</font>

5
00:00:18.090 --> 00:00:19.830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's so funny?!</font>

6
00:00:21.320 --> 00:00:23.930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! You listening to me?!</font>

7
00:00:21.850 --> 00:00:26.640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm starting to get a handle on what 
kind of person ends up as the spellcaster.</font>

8
00:00:24.340 --> 00:00:25.500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Sorry. sorry...</font>

9
00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:28.650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Stop laughing! Stop laughing. damn it!</font>

10
00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:28.970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">New one feels a lot like the old one.</font>

11
00:00:28.970 --> 00:00:32.600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their whimsy is unstoppable.</font>

12
00:00:34.210 --> 00:00:36.750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's start over. I'm Remlin.</font>

13
00:00:36.750 --> 00:00:39.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As the new spellcaster. I hope to p—</font>

14
00:00:39.650 --> 00:00:40.770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean. work well with you!</font>

15
00:00:41.120 --> 00:00:42.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you almost say "play"?</font>

16
00:00:42.130 --> 00:00:44.490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many spellcasters 
have there been. anyway?</font>

17
00:00:44.490 --> 00:00:47.370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I believe Remlin would be the sixth.</font>

18
00:00:47.370 --> 00:00:48.610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You <i>believe</i>?</font>

19
00:00:49.010 --> 00:00:54.460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They tell their histories through art. 
not the written word.</font>

20
00:00:56.100 --> 00:00:59.700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So. hey. there's this thing I noticed.</font>

21
00:00:59.700 --> 00:01:04.540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I draw on a person. the power doesn't 
work right if I don't have their consent.</font>

22
00:01:05.070 --> 00:01:08.650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Outside of town. I usually get permission 
before I draw on the walls.</font>

23
00:01:08.650 --> 00:01:10.290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it's probably the same thing.</font>

24
00:01:10.290 --> 00:01:13.810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figure if you need permission 
to draw on walls and objects.</font>

25
00:01:13.810 --> 00:01:17.090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it goes double for people. right?</font>

26
00:01:17.090 --> 00:01:19.640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's how it was with Gob. yeah.</font>

27
00:01:19.640 --> 00:01:22.830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do spellcasters get the same 
abilities as their predecessors?</font>

28
00:01:22.830 --> 00:01:26.200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard their powers have 
historically been similar.</font>

29
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:29.150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you sometimes see subtle differences.</font>

30
00:01:29.580 --> 00:01:33.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone has their own way of using things. 
their own experiences and ideas.</font>

31
00:01:34.340 --> 00:01:38.690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makes sense that everyone's ability 
would take a different shape.</font>

32
00:01:39.010 --> 00:01:42.280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if it's the same each generation.
I guess it's the vital instrument that's spec—</font>

33
00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. that's not it.</font>

34
00:01:44.070 --> 00:01:48.550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It turns out the same 'cause we all bring 
a real sense of play to our drawing.</font>

35
00:01:48.550 --> 00:01:52.840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We draw balloons in a stressful scene 
or flowers in a combat scene...</font>

36
00:01:52.840 --> 00:01:57.670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We sneak all kinds of meaning 
into our drawings to play around.</font>

37
00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:01.770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Freedom and play"...</font>

38
00:02:01.770 --> 00:02:05.880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think those are the factors Gob and 
those before him were chosen for.</font>

39
00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:08.370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll probably choose someone like that too.</font>

40
00:02:08.370 --> 00:02:09.530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love it!</font>

41
00:02:10.210 --> 00:02:12.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah. I don't get it.</i></font>

42
00:02:12.930 --> 00:02:14.470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what it comes down to is.</font>

43
00:02:14.470 --> 00:02:17.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you end up with similar powers 
because you think the same way?</font>

44
00:02:18.500 --> 00:02:20.410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't think the same way!</font>

45
00:02:20.410 --> 00:02:23.160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all draw whatever 
<i>we</i> want to in the moment!</font>

46
00:02:23.160 --> 00:02:25.370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we end up drawing is different. too!</font>

47
00:02:29.680 --> 00:02:31.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lay off. Enjin.</font>

48
00:02:31.130 --> 00:02:33.530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you try to go too deep 
into conversation with an artist.</font>

49
00:02:33.530 --> 00:02:34.880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll just end up more confused.</font>

50
00:02:34.880 --> 00:02:37.140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Enjin's bothered by it.</i></font>

51
00:02:39.700 --> 00:02:44.270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want me to draw "reduce damage 
from one major hit" on your body. right?</font>

52
00:02:44.740 --> 00:02:46.320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Coming right up!</font>

53
00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:53.280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-H-H-Hey!</font>

54
00:02:54.450 --> 00:02:55.850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're tattooing it?!</font>

55
00:02:55.850 --> 00:02:59.040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remlin. Take this serious—</font>

56
00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:00.450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. what?</font>

57
00:03:00.870 --> 00:03:04.440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You turned the instrument into a brush before.</font>

58
00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:06.120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with that shape?</font>

59
00:03:06.490 --> 00:03:09.790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was just thinking it'd make a cool tattoo. 
and it turned into this.</font>

60
00:03:09.790 --> 00:03:12.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to have options. right?</font>

61
00:03:12.130 --> 00:03:14.530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. you kidding me?</font>

62
00:03:14.530 --> 00:03:19.350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not only can you cast spells. 
you can also create any tool you want?!</font>

63
00:03:19.350 --> 00:03:21.820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're terrifying!</font>

64
00:03:23.020 --> 00:03:26.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine. fine. No tattoos.</font>

65
00:03:26.030 --> 00:03:29.200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I just draw it on. 
it'll wash off in water. right?</font>

66
00:03:29.630 --> 00:03:31.570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So let's do this right.</font>

67
00:03:35.530 --> 00:03:39.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can scribb—I mean. 
cast a spell on your body. right?</font>

68
00:03:41.090 --> 00:03:43.080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This kid never stops.</i></font>

69
00:03:43.660 --> 00:03:46.720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This kid's kinda growing on me.</font>

70
00:03:53.330 --> 00:03:56.380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the help. Mr. Mayor. Remlin.</font>

71
00:03:56.380 --> 00:04:00.340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well. I'm sorry for the runaround.</font>

72
00:04:00.940 --> 00:04:05.470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think drawing on nine people 
really took a toll on the kid.</font>

73
00:04:05.470 --> 00:04:08.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good work for a first time.</font>

74
00:04:08.130 --> 00:04:09.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks a lot.</font>

75
00:04:20.340 --> 00:04:22.110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here. Mr. Mayor?!</font>

76
00:04:22.110 --> 00:04:24.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't pass the pen to some no-name brat!</font>

77
00:04:24.950 --> 00:04:27.770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should go to someone more worthy!</font>

78
00:04:27.770 --> 00:04:29.960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The guys who couldn't come in.</i></font>

79
00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:34.010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won the Perfect Art Contest!</font>

80
00:04:34.010 --> 00:04:38.580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tons of people were counting on me 
to become the new spellcaster.</font>

81
00:04:38.580 --> 00:04:42.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I came all the way out here. 
and this is how you treat me?!</font>

82
00:04:42.390 --> 00:04:44.640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Canvas Town's really gone downhill!</font>

83
00:04:44.640 --> 00:04:47.220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway. I'm a better art—</font>

84
00:04:47.220 --> 00:04:48.230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

85
00:04:49.380 --> 00:04:53.230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your shitty attitude is the reason 
you can't even enter the city!</font>

86
00:04:53.230 --> 00:04:58.320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't need posers who call themselves 
artists but only care about fame!</font>

87
00:04:58.570 --> 00:05:01.500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get that through your heads and make tracks!</font>

88
00:05:01.500 --> 00:05:03.870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No one wants to look at your ugly faces!</font>

89
00:05:07.230 --> 00:05:11.370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man. the mayor's always scary when he's mad.</font>

90
00:05:17.750 --> 00:05:19.840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you guys.</font>

91
00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:22.510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get so mad that 
you pop a blood vessel. okay?</font>

92
00:05:22.930 --> 00:05:24.230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry.</font>

93
00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:27.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just stay away from the gate. Mr. Mayor.</font>

94
00:05:28.160 --> 00:05:31.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks. I'm glad I saw all that.</font>

95
00:05:31.390 --> 00:05:32.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be back.</font>

96
00:05:34.330 --> 00:05:37.240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll come to draw at Cleaner HQ someday too!</font>

97
00:05:39.070 --> 00:05:40.570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bye-bee!</font>

98
00:05:50.850 --> 00:05:53.200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are we going back to Cleaner HQ?</font>

99
00:05:53.200 --> 00:05:56.670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. To get your full-face.</font>

100
00:05:58.390 --> 00:06:00.170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But first. Rudo...</font>

101
00:06:00.690 --> 00:06:03.680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's pick you up a treat.</font>

102
00:06:04.470 --> 00:06:05.770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A treat?</font>

103
00:06:11.530 --> 00:06:13.630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Hey...</font>

104
00:06:13.630 --> 00:06:14.690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You sure?</font>

105
00:06:15.250 --> 00:06:20.690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never hurts to be prepared. 
so pick out a few things that sing to you.</font>

106
00:06:20.950 --> 00:06:24.910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're far from the polluted zones. 
so no trash beasts here.</font>

107
00:06:24.910 --> 00:06:27.510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take some time and pick out what you—</font>

108
00:06:33.980 --> 00:06:35.540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome! Awesome! Awesome!</font>

109
00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:36.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome!</font>

110
00:06:36.010 --> 00:06:39.040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He really loves this stuff. huh?</font>

111
00:08:30.570 --> 00:08:31.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's done!</font>

112
00:08:31.950 --> 00:08:33.620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell yeah. it's done!</font>

113
00:08:33.620 --> 00:08:36.200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's done! I did it!</font>

114
00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:38.580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I freaking did it!</font>

115
00:08:38.850 --> 00:08:39.830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who's that?</font>

116
00:08:39.830 --> 00:08:43.290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. you're here. Welcome back.</font>

117
00:08:43.860 --> 00:08:47.060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got word about what 
happened in Canvas Town.</font>

118
00:08:47.060 --> 00:08:48.590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry to hear about—</font>

119
00:08:48.590 --> 00:08:49.630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there!</font>

120
00:08:50.650 --> 00:08:52.070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mask's ready!</font>

121
00:08:53.950 --> 00:08:56.010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. that guy.</font>

122
00:08:56.310 --> 00:09:00.940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's August. He makes the Cleaners' gear.</font>

123
00:09:01.390 --> 00:09:04.940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like he finished your full-face. Rudo.</font>

124
00:09:04.940 --> 00:09:07.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! It's freaking finished!</font>

125
00:09:07.030 --> 00:09:09.720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It came out perfect. man!</font>

126
00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:13.660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't have time to meet up. but I got 
his measurements while he was asleep.</font>

127
00:09:13.660 --> 00:09:15.930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so it should just fit!</font>

128
00:09:15.930 --> 00:09:19.610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Enjin and Semiu told me 
about his personality.</font>

129
00:09:19.610 --> 00:09:21.750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I made some choices 
to max out the cool factor!</font>

130
00:09:22.060 --> 00:09:23.200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait a minute.</font>

131
00:09:23.570 --> 00:09:26.750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He got my measurements... 
while I was asleep?</font>

132
00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:30.140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lucky me that you didn't lock your room!</font>

133
00:09:30.510 --> 00:09:32.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You asshole!</font>

134
00:09:32.130 --> 00:09:34.620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sphereites don't lock their doors?</font>

135
00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:37.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man. and Rudo doesn't sleep that much.</font>

136
00:09:37.990 --> 00:09:40.730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It takes real skill to 
catch him when he's asleep!</font>

137
00:09:40.730 --> 00:09:42.740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Riyo. how do you know that?</font>

138
00:09:42.740 --> 00:09:44.150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Big brother!</font>

139
00:09:44.150 --> 00:09:46.860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. li'l sis!</font>

140
00:09:46.860 --> 00:09:48.980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to stop doing this!</font>

141
00:09:48.980 --> 00:09:52.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop causing trouble for everyone!</font>

142
00:09:52.030 --> 00:09:54.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What was that?!</font>

143
00:09:54.050 --> 00:09:55.810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And please keep your voice down.</font>

144
00:09:55.810 --> 00:09:56.780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was that?!</font>

145
00:09:56.780 --> 00:09:57.720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please!</font>

146
00:09:57.720 --> 00:10:00.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eishia. sweetie! You here?</font>

147
00:09:58.740 --> 00:10:00.800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're siblings?</i></font>

148
00:10:00.130 --> 00:10:00.800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am!</font>

149
00:10:00.800 --> 00:10:01.600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where are you? Hey!</font>

150
00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:02.790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm right here!</font>

151
00:10:11.950 --> 00:10:15.800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man. What's with Ground people 
shouting all the time?</font>

152
00:10:16.060 --> 00:10:17.680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You're one to talk.</i></font>

153
00:10:18.860 --> 00:10:20.170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Rudo.</font>

154
00:10:20.170 --> 00:10:22.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take off your choker a minute.</font>

155
00:10:31.820 --> 00:10:32.900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you—</font>

156
00:10:35.210 --> 00:10:37.910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on. Hold out the choker.</font>

157
00:10:44.040 --> 00:10:48.240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Choker." It's like a communicator...</font>

158
00:10:48.240 --> 00:10:49.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kind of like a phone.</font>

159
00:10:49.950 --> 00:10:53.420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can talk through it to people 
you've traded blood with.</font>

160
00:10:53.420 --> 00:10:57.470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that why Ground people all wear 
these things around your necks?</font>

161
00:10:58.050 --> 00:11:01.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And trading blood gives it a real 
friends-to-the-end feel. right?</font>

162
00:11:01.950 --> 00:11:04.610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Contact us any time. Rudo.</font>

163
00:11:04.610 --> 00:11:05.550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure...</font>

164
00:11:07.440 --> 00:11:09.580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What tech is this?</i></font>

165
00:11:09.580 --> 00:11:12.740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait. It's not another Giver power. is it?</i></font>

166
00:11:13.320 --> 00:11:15.110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway...</font>

167
00:11:16.690 --> 00:11:19.620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll be taking some of <i>your</i> blood too!</font>

168
00:11:25.090 --> 00:11:29.150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At last. we're off to No Man's Land 
to find the lady!</font>

169
00:11:29.150 --> 00:11:30.880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said...</font>

170
00:11:31.260 --> 00:11:34.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't think you brought 
a little too much trash?</font>

171
00:11:34.030 --> 00:11:35.880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have to walk at some point.</font>

172
00:11:36.280 --> 00:11:38.740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just take what you can carry.</font>

173
00:11:39.160 --> 00:11:40.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all backups.</font>

174
00:11:41.890 --> 00:11:45.460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be your second time 
in a No Man's Land. I guess.</font>

175
00:11:45.460 --> 00:11:47.900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The trouble's going to start 
the second we arrive.</font>

176
00:11:48.450 --> 00:11:49.800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Better be ready.</font>

177
00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:05.580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Penta. the desert No Man's Land.</font>

178
00:12:07.800 --> 00:12:09.330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that's exciting.</font>

179
00:12:09.370 --> 00:12:13.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b><font size="8">Episode 10</font></b></font>

180
00:12:09.370 --> 00:12:13.340
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="35">"Penta: The Desert No Man's Land"</font></b></font>

181
00:12:20.620 --> 00:12:23.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sand? No...</font>

182
00:12:23.050 --> 00:12:25.230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Waste matter worn down to dust?</font>

183
00:12:34.800 --> 00:12:37.490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And here they come.</font>

184
00:12:37.890 --> 00:12:42.480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Witness reports say the woman 
should live further in.</font>

185
00:12:42.480 --> 00:12:44.760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you keep up. Rudo.</font>

186
00:12:46.120 --> 00:12:47.780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the plan.</font>

187
00:12:50.930 --> 00:12:55.000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use those gloves—3R—to beat them down.</font>

188
00:12:58.010 --> 00:12:59.900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then we'll go find the woman.</font>

189
00:13:03.210 --> 00:13:05.680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's start with some warm-ups!</font>

190
00:13:05.940 --> 00:13:08.180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This might be fun.</font>

191
00:13:13.700 --> 00:13:15.160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get it?!</font>

192
00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:19.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In a No Man's Land. first. 
you put on the half-mask!</font>

193
00:13:19.490 --> 00:13:22.490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You connect it to your oxygen tank!</font>

194
00:13:23.870 --> 00:13:26.190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You put the mask on overtop and...</font>

195
00:13:26.190 --> 00:13:27.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got yourself a full-face!</font>

196
00:13:40.550 --> 00:13:43.680
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b><font size="40"><font color="#e7e9e6">The Cleaning Begins</font></font></b></font>

197
00:13:47.330 --> 00:13:50.310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Penta. the desert No Man's Land?</font>

198
00:13:50.600 --> 00:13:53.310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that where it is. boss?</font>

199
00:13:53.690 --> 00:13:55.670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other one...</font>

200
00:13:59.820 --> 00:14:01.450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll see when you go.</font>

201
00:14:06.410 --> 00:14:09.950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. let's get this down.</font>

202
00:14:10.230 --> 00:14:13.730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First trash beast encountered upon 
arrival in No Man's Land Penta.</font>

203
00:14:13.730 --> 00:14:15.910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shape was "scorpion-like."</font>

204
00:14:15.910 --> 00:14:20.670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Appearance and thickness of exoskeleton 
suggest attacks like a scorpion.</font>

205
00:14:20.670 --> 00:14:24.010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pincer and tail attacks presumed...</font>

206
00:14:24.010 --> 00:14:25.020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

207
00:15:01.450 --> 00:15:03.510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. I didn't do it.</font>

208
00:15:07.270 --> 00:15:09.430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh. keep it down.</font>

209
00:16:16.010 --> 00:16:18.790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Octashredder!</font>

210
00:16:41.330 --> 00:16:43.230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Missed one. huh?</font>

211
00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:46.070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up to you now.</font>

212
00:17:42.790 --> 00:17:44.960
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b></b><font size="40"><font color="#c7cbc8">"Asshole"</font></font></font>

213
00:17:52.870 --> 00:17:56.040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lots of those scorpion trash beasts.</font>

214
00:17:56.340 --> 00:17:58.060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For them to come out on the surface suggests</font>

215
00:17:58.060 --> 00:18:03.700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a whole lot of trash buried 
beneath this sand-like stuff.</font>

216
00:18:06.050 --> 00:18:07.100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tomme!</font>

217
00:18:07.540 --> 00:18:11.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your record-keeping duties are important. 
but do them after combat's over!</font>

218
00:18:11.050 --> 00:18:12.380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was so dangerous!</font>

219
00:18:13.200 --> 00:18:14.780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I should.</font>

220
00:18:14.780 --> 00:18:17.780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if I'd waited. I'd probably forget.</font>

221
00:18:19.290 --> 00:18:24.110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides. your job here in No-Man's Land 
is to protect the record-keeper. right?</font>

222
00:18:24.110 --> 00:18:25.760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I trust you guys.</font>

223
00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:28.800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still. have <i>some</i> self-preservation instinct!</font>

224
00:18:46.810 --> 00:18:49.020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is there something there?</i></font>

225
00:18:49.560 --> 00:18:51.570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. there you are!</font>

226
00:18:55.090 --> 00:18:57.160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delmon! Tamsy!</font>

227
00:18:57.160 --> 00:18:59.300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kicked up a lot of sand. eh?</font>

228
00:18:59.300 --> 00:19:00.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We almost lost sight of you.</font>

229
00:19:00.990 --> 00:19:04.710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good back there. Rudo!</font>

230
00:19:04.710 --> 00:19:08.520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only wish I could've seen you in action!</font>

231
00:19:08.520 --> 00:19:10.750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure we will soon enough.</font>

232
00:19:10.750 --> 00:19:12.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah. but still!</font>

233
00:19:12.360 --> 00:19:16.640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad. I managed to be 
a little useful this time.</font>

234
00:19:12.990 --> 00:19:16.640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Well. next time. try to stay close...</font>

235
00:19:28.100 --> 00:19:32.250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes... of course that's how it is...</font>

236
00:19:35.870 --> 00:19:40.370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You came here to see Amo. didn't you?</font>

237
00:19:44.850 --> 00:19:46.130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long...</font>

238
00:19:47.370 --> 00:19:50.930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How long has that woman been there?</font>

239
00:19:50.930 --> 00:19:55.170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know it's hard to see around here. 
but I couldn't sense her either!</font>

240
00:19:56.140 --> 00:19:59.140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. Could she be...</font>

241
00:19:59.430 --> 00:20:02.860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think she's the one we're looking for?</font>

242
00:20:03.510 --> 00:20:06.450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. no way it's that easy.</font>

243
00:20:06.450 --> 00:20:09.520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She doesn't seem hostile to me. at least.</font>

244
00:20:09.520 --> 00:20:12.180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe we should ask for directions?</font>

245
00:20:12.520 --> 00:20:13.810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

246
00:20:14.200 --> 00:20:18.780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You the one who's seen people coming 
and going from the Sphere and the Ground?!</font>

247
00:20:18.780 --> 00:20:20.740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show some manners!</font>

248
00:20:22.220 --> 00:20:24.080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh. yes. indeed!</font>

249
00:20:24.470 --> 00:20:28.180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? She's the woman we've been looking for!</font>

250
00:20:29.890 --> 00:20:33.030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well... Guess we got lucky.</font>

251
00:20:33.030 --> 00:20:34.760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's talk to her and get go—</font>

252
00:20:35.460 --> 00:20:36.690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

253
00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:41.390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It stinks out here. 
It's not good for the lungs.</font>

254
00:20:41.790 --> 00:20:45.150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps any talking should 
be done at Amo's house?</font>

255
00:20:45.150 --> 00:20:47.990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Masks won't be needed there.</font>

256
00:20:49.180 --> 00:20:51.890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't she bring a mask. then?</font>

257
00:20:51.890 --> 00:20:54.050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's such a short walk!</font>

258
00:20:54.050 --> 00:20:55.830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay? Okay?</font>

259
00:20:56.240 --> 00:20:57.240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enjin.</font>

260
00:20:57.820 --> 00:21:01.240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't I go and ask her what's what?</font>

261
00:21:02.520 --> 00:21:04.710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah. we should all go.</font>

262
00:21:04.710 --> 00:21:10.500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if she's plotting something. 
I'd prefer to talk it out.</font>

263
00:21:10.500 --> 00:21:14.330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we end up in a fight anyway. 
I'll take her on.</font>

264
00:21:14.330 --> 00:21:16.550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. you sure?</font>

265
00:21:16.550 --> 00:21:19.360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hold back the best.</font>

266
00:21:57.450 --> 00:21:59.020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way...</font>

267
00:22:02.160 --> 00:22:03.210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How...</font>
